		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That thing is 100% definitely a clone, but what is called a superclone that uses exact copies of the original chips (same pinout too !).<br /><br />And what you experience is definitely too weak power supply. You need at least 1A (the more the merrier) and more than 7V (but less than 18V).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


